    <section>
      <h3>My Belief</h3>
      <p>Perfume is not just a scent — it is the soul of nature captured in time. Every drop of attar I make carries stories of the ocean wind, the warmth of sunlight, and the breath of flowers. I believe that true perfumery is not learned in classrooms, but felt through the heart.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>My Process</h3>
      <p>I blend ancient and natural techniques passed through generations:</p>
      <ul style="line-height:1.8; font-size:1.1rem;">
        <li>🌞 Solar infusion to absorb the flower’s warmth and energy.</li>
        <li>💧 Steam distillation to capture the purest molecules of aroma.</li>
        <li>🕊️ Fusion aging to unite oil, water, and spirit into harmony.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Every fragrance is aged under silence, prayer, and respect for nature’s rhythm.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>My Signature</h3>
      <p>Each attar I create holds a memory — of sunlight over the sea, of roses kissed by morning dew, of ambergris born from the deep. My perfumes are alcohol-free, hand-crafted, and made with devotion. This is not chemistry — it is alchemy guided by heart.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>My Promise</h3>
      <p>To create scents that speak of purity, tradition, and emotion. To honor the earth that gives us flowers, and to remind the world that luxury is simplicity touched by soul.</p>
